  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to identify the predisposing factors, epidemiological features
      and clinical and microbiological diagnosis of infectious keratitis in two public referral
      centers of ophthalmology in a countryside city of Brazil.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
